{"id": 902, "genre": 1001, "title": "你们所谓的“man”到底指的是什么？", "description": "外表兄贵，八块腐基。（题图来自：Nicolas Dehghani）", "record_count": 3577, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183708iZfcFP9wnv2KxMpr.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-30T10:52:16Z", "options": [{"id": 62720, "content": "内心强大，处事不惊，不以物喜不以己悲", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473962}, {"id": 181249, "content": "演员靳东 就是男人该有的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971162}, {"id": 62721, "content": "管得了员工 修得了汽车 练得了腹肌 醉酒公主抱 敢壁咚懂收手 可能有点直男癌", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539928}, {"id": 62722, "content": "很有气场", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165309}, {"id": 63490, "content": "幽默，有责任心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546632}, {"id": 62724, "content": "每天都去健身的坚持，尊重女性，重感情，关键是有上进心", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529495}, {"id": 62725, "content": "绅士", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519526}, {"id": 62981, "content": "有担当", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541481}, {"id": 62727, "content": "就是我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403368}, {"id": 62728, "content": "难道不是一种性欲么。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192911Ug0WZMDlfFAndSqT.jpg", "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539945}, {"id": 62729, "content": "知道怎么尊重女性，知道什么时候该做决定，知道并且这么做", "image": null, "praise_count": 343, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539930}, {"id": 62730, "content": "抱起来站着操", "image": null, "praise_count": 225, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198262}, {"id": 65034, "content": "不惹事 不怕事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 556283}, {"id": 62731, "content": "遇事不退缩，敢于承担！", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539952}, {"id": 62732, "content": "说的是我吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525157}, {"id": 62733, "content": "超人就是man", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193343iyv53t28ICLzsDl0.jpg", "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539955}, {"id": 62734, "content": "有气魄，有担当\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538355}, {"id": 62735, "content": "不娘就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519008}, {"id": 62736, "content": "会玩会工作 会疯会生活 会下厨会运动 会爱会做梦", "image": "img/option/option/201607021830033JpscN1KqB5VWDgC.jpg", "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110383}, {"id": 66577, "content": "有责任感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564075}, {"id": 62737, "content": "有见识 有胸怀 看着他有安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412955}, {"id": 62739, "content": "财大器粗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518145}, {"id": 62740, "content": "会让你绝望，但永远值得被相信。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531762}, {"id": 62741, "content": "粗旷的大手还有强有力的大腿外加强逻辑低语速的谈话方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539989}, {"id": 62742, "content": "有担当，有想法，积极上进。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 526974}, {"id": 62743, "content": "敢扶跌倒的老奶奶，不迟疑一秒的那种!!! ", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149680}, {"id": 64023, "content": "是我楼上舞蹈班班长的男旁友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549414}, {"id": 62744, "content": "络腮胡 褶子脸 薄唇 深邃的眼神 d罩杯胸肌 八块馒头腹肌 胸毛腹毛腿毛各种毛 大臭脚 大粗腿 ", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161506s35qoNtLRDT1bQxn.jpg", "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497662}, {"id": 74521, "content": "有威严有能力行动力，但会尊重任何人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595067}, {"id": 62745, "content": "安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522021}, {"id": 62747, "content": "不是可以指任何人么，像As a man sows, so shall he reap. 种瓜得瓜，种豆得豆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534080}, {"id": 63259, "content": "胸怀宽广", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 544201}, {"id": 62748, "content": "有责任心加上做事果断", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254572}, {"id": 62749, "content": "全身心投入，敢于承担！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246984}, {"id": 62750, "content": "收放自如", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540011}, {"id": 63262, "content": "认真 外出宅家一个样 清爽 温暖 运动阳光 有想法 有干劲", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 544194}, {"id": 63007, "content": "不穿贴身黑色小脚裤搭配黑色尖头皮鞋..(-_^)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142862}, {"id": 62752, "content": "女朋友问塑料袋还要不要！我没说话，抓起来就扔垃圾桶了。女朋友觉得我好man", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540023}, {"id": 65569, "content": "有求必硬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552727}, {"id": 63009, "content": "干净，克制，敏锐，煽动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539557}, {"id": 62754, "content": "帅到抖题啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529453}, {"id": 62755, "content": "不盲目，敢担当，有本事，床上功夫好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529508}, {"id": 62757, "content": "不磨叽，有主见，有型～", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522874}, {"id": 62758, "content": "慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"i